org.apache.lucene.geo

Class XYLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.geo.XYGeometry
      • org.apache.lucene.geo.XYLine

  • public class XYLine
extends XYGeometry
    Represents a line in cartesian space. You can construct the Line directly with float[], float[] x, y arrays coordinates.
